<subSubSection box="[185,879,413,439]" pageId="6" pageNumber="83" type="distribution">
<paragraph box="[185,879,413,439]" pageId="6" pageNumber="83">Known distribution: West Malaysia (Pahang) (Paulian 1977).</paragraph>
